# Illusion of Wearing

Welcome to the "Illusion of Wearing" project repository â€“ a Python script for virtual clothing overlay on live webcam feed.

## Overview

This script utilizes computer vision and deep learning to detect key body points and overlays virtual clothing items such as shirts and pants on a person in real-time through a webcam feed.

## Requirements

- Python 3.x
- OpenCV
- MXNet
- GluonCV
- imutils
- NumPy
- tqdm
- Matplotlib

## Usage

1. Install the required dependencies:

   ```bash
   pip install opencv-python mxnet gluoncv imutils numpy tqdm matplotlib

## Getting Started

1. **Clone the Repository:**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/AmmarAsif-cmd/illusion-of-wearing.git
